    "description": "<p>ELECTRONIC SYNERGIES is a Singapore-based business-to-business supplier commercial and industrial customized products. With over 10 years of experience in this specialisation under our belt, we not only know what we are doing, but also experts in this field.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Leveraging on a hard-earned expertise that span analog, digital and high frequency applications, our core competencies cover OEM, including module and system integration, as well as the design and manufacture of molded interconnection cables, printed circuit boards, and box-built assemblies.</p>",
